    <!--3 paragraphs  -->
    <p><em>Paradise Island</em> is a tropical paradise located in the heart of the Pacific Ocean.
         With its crystal-clear waters and lush landscapes, 
         it's a dream destination for travelers seeking <b>relaxation</b> and <strong>adventure</strong>. 
         Whether you want to unwind on sun-kissed beaches or 
         embark on thrilling outdoor activities, Paradise Island has something for everyone.
        </p>
        <p>Paradise Island is a secluded oasis, far removed from the hustle
             and bustle of everyday life. The air is filled with the sweet scent
              of tropical flowers, and the gentle rustle of palm leaves provides
               a soothing soundtrack to your escape. As you step onto the shores, 
               you are greeted by the warm embrace of the tropical sun and the rhythmic 
               lull of the ocean waves.

        </p>
        <p>The coral reefs that surround Paradise Island are a kaleidoscope of colors, 
            housing an abundance of marine life that beckons snorkelers and divers
             to explore their vibrant underwater world. From playful dolphins to 
             graceful sea turtles, the marine inhabitants add to the allure of this aquatic paradise

        </p>
